{"title":"国庆节之夜月亮与太阳对话  调寄《满江红》","authors":["郭沫若"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":10,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"国庆节之夜月亮与太阳对话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——调寄《满江红》——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（月亮）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国庆良宵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月华我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神抖擞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢愉如昼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光柱千寻天网大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹花万簇锦屏秀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今在北美洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能见否？（太阳）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪能够！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白宫外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人牵狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向黑人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎面扑胸张口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血肉横飞天地暗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水龙乱扫妖魔吼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果然呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地狱在人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花旗丑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六三年十月九日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}